profile_positions.description:
Working as a projectmanager/tendermanager on various, mostly port, dike strengthening and infrastructure related projects. Activities include design and projectmanagement in the tender and execution for projects and structures like quay walls, jetties, steel bridges, marine steel structures, dike strengthening structures, underground structures, building pits and foundations.

Projectmanagement for projects include: underground extension of national museum Maurithuis The Hague, steel pedestrian bridges crossing platforms and tracks at Roosendaal station, offshore test frame platform for Pioneering Spirit, quaywall extension and jetty seagoing tankers Argos plant Rotterdam, diaphragm wall dike strengthening Krimpen a/d Lek, underground extension of national museum Palace Het Loo Apeldoorn and foundation and building pit for highrise project HAUT Amsterdam.

Tenders for projects include: rail-road bridge De Haandrik, near shore wind turbine foundations IJsselmeer, strengthening mast foundations power line Hoogeveen-Vierverlaten, Second Opening bridge foundations Poole UK, building pit A4 highway tunnel Rotterdam, dike strengthening BAS Bergambacht-Schoonhoven and KIJK Krimpen a/d IJssel, renovation historical quaywall Prinsessewal The Hague and many others.
